PINELLAS COUNTY, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Thomas M. WALSH, Jr., et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4891 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 01, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellees' motion to dismiss appeal is granted. This appeal is dismissed as from a nonappealable nonfinal order.

LaROSE, C.J., and VILLANTI and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
